OL,3,CRetail sales boost of 2.5% 'barely
OL,4,Ctouching the sides' of costs, sector
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FJuly retail sales were up 2.5% on a
OL,8,Fyear ago but growth is "barely
OL,9,Ftouching the sides" of covering the
OL,10,Flast budget's #7 billion in new costs
OL,11,Fon the sector, bosses have warned.
OL,13,FThe uptick in the UK's total retail
OL,14,Fsales was against growth of 0.5% last
OL,15,FJuly and the 12-month average growth
OL,16,Fof 1.9%, according to British Retail
OL,17,FConsortium (BRC)-KPMG data.
