OL,3,CRetail sales boost of 2.5% 'barely
OL,4,Ctouching the sides' of costs, sector
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FNon-food sales increased by 1.4%
OL,8,Fagainst a decline of 1.8% last July,
OL,9,Fwith figures showing fashion sold well
OL,10,Fearly in the month but deteriorated as
OL,11,Fweather worsened, while homeware and
OL,12,Findoor furniture sales grew steadily,
OL,13,Frecovering from the previous year's
OL,14,Fdecline.
OL,16,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,17,Fsaid: "With sales growth at these
OL,18,Flevels, it is barely touching the
OL,19,Fsides of covering the #7 billion new
OL,20,Fcosts imposed on retailers at the last
OL,21,FBudget.
