OL,3,CRetail sales boost of 2.5% 'barely
OL,4,Ctouching the sides' of costs, sector
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"If the upcoming Autumn Budget sees
OL,8,Fmore taxes levied on retailers'
OL,9,Fshoulders, many will be forced to make
OL,10,Fdifficult choices about the future of
OL,11,Fshops and jobs, and ongoing pressure
OL,12,Fwould push prices higher.
OL,14,F"Ultimately, this means more families
OL,15,Fstruggling, particularly those on
OL,16,Flower incomes, reduced consumer
OL,17,Fspending and a drag on economic
OL,18,Fgrowth."
