OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FPharmacy, health and beauty performed
OL,8,Fstrongly, up 9.8%, while continuing to
OL,9,Fbenefit from the enduring post-Covid
OL,10,F"lipstick effect" ` where shoppers
OL,11,Fturn to small and affordable luxuries
OL,12,Fto boost their mood, Barclays said.
OL,14,FHowever, confidence in the strength of
OL,15,Fthe UK economy dipped once again in
OL,16,FJuly, falling three points month-on-
OL,17,Fmonth to 22%, the lowest level seen
OL,18,Fsince January's 21%.
