OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FKaren Johnson, head of retail at
OL,8,FBarclays, said: "The summer sales,
OL,9,Fchangeable weather and shoppers
OL,10,Fseeking the "feel-good factor" led to
OL,11,Fa strong July for retailers,
OL,12,Fparticularly among beauty, clothing
OL,13,Fand furniture stores.
OL,15,F"While confidence in the UK economy
OL,16,Fremains subdued, prudent money
OL,17,Fmanagement, supported by the growing
OL,18,Fpopularity of AI tools to help with
OL,19,Fbudgeting, is contributing to a
OL,20,Fcontinued resilience in personal and
OL,21,Fhousehold finances."
